## Tasks
- Learn Tailscale concepts
- Create a small test setup
- Connect two devices you own
- Verify secure access to one internal service
- Document:
  - what problem Tailscale solves
  - what it does not solve

## Deliverable
- Tailscale notes + simple topology diagram

## Checkpoint
