## Theory
Learn:
- captive portals
- evil twin risks
- local network exposure
- VPN use on untrusted networks
- DNS/privacy basics on public Wi-Fi

## Tasks
Create a personal travel checklist:
- before connecting
- while connecting
- after connecting
- what to avoid
- when to use hotspot instead
- when to use Tailscale/VPN
- whether to carry a travel router

Write a one-page decision guide:
- hotel Wi-Fi vs phone hotspot
- direct connect vs travel router
- always-on VPN/Tailscale usage

## Deliverable
- travel network safety checklist

## Checkpoint
Do I have a repeatable plan for hotel/public network use?

